<br>
HP regeneration items (like aura of health or aura of battle or whatever) work in similar fashion, except the cap is 30 (which is even harder to reach than FT15).  Attack items (like aura of battle or vengeance) also stack, but the cap is 250 attack (aob is +10, vengeance is +5 per level, so veng 2 = +10), and the attack increases from the avatar buff (+100 attack) count against the limit.<br>
<br>
But back on topic, the solstice earrings have some of the best stats you'll find on any earring, and the FT1 is a great bonus.  I'd be happy to help with any combines that I can--I recently hit 200 in fishing (the max), so I could combine fishing poles if anyone has the parts.  Several of my other tradeskills are in the 185-195 range, but I think if you ask around, there will be Arrows with even higher skills in those tradeskills. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=445044" target="top">Xenophon</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->, 65 Paladin<br>
